description.plain:
“Natural” is a track that feels perfect for a road trip, a track that hums away with a driving beat, culminating in the sheer excitement of finally having a night alone with someone you’ve loved for a while, among many highs and lows.

As described on Tanukichan’s bandcamp

annotations:
Everything’s color
 Everything, you know, is
 Oh, it must be to do with orange

This sample is taken from LSD—The Beyond Within, a 1986 BBC television documentary which explored the rise and fall of the hallucinogenic drug LSD. This pairs with the song’s drug themes and its psychedelic and distorted guitar riff.
